  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\n        \n\n    \n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe only way to afford the PTO for a decent vacation is by digging deep into your own morally-grey pocket. Many of you would do anything for a little extra PTO. After a long, hard week in the workplace, a vacation starts to seem like the only antidote for a poisonous job and a collection of mean coworkers. Even with dreams of white sand, turquoise beaches, and an all-inclusive swim-up bar dancing in your head, there is still a limit to what we\u0026#39;d do for a trip. \u0026#34;\u003ca href=\"https://cheezburger.com/41448709/25-lord-of-the-rings-memes-for-middle-earth-couples-on-a-romantic-walk-to-mordor-july-14-2025\"\u003eWould I do \u003ci\u003eanything\u003c/i\u003e for a vacation?\u003c/a\u003e\u0026#34; you wonder.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBut there\u0026#39;s a line in the sand of common decency that mustn\u0026#39;t be crossed, even for the sake of a well-deserved vacay.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\n    \u003cli\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHowever, for some, the desperate and the morally grey, ethics hardly matter when it comes to PTO. This woman has only endured 6 months of 2025 but has already spent her annual PTO, and in a shocking turn of events, she spilled the beans on the immoral lengths that she was willing to go to get a few more days off—even if it meant disrespecting everyone in the office with a diabolical lie.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528732928/h2DCFF65A\" id=\"_r_a_10528732928\" width=\"800\" height=\"420\" alt=\"Cheezburger Image 10528732928\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe image does not depict the actual subjects of the story. Subjects are models.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528728832/hC9C86D2A/faked-my-own-pregnancy-pto-sitting-on-packed-commuter-train-overheard-two-coworkers-talking-behind\" id=\"_r_a_10528728832\" width=\"454\" height=\"285\" alt=\"Overheard on the train, \u0026#34;I faked my own pregnancy... for the PTO\u0026#34; I was sitting on a packed commuter train when I overheard two coworkers talking behind me.\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528729856/h9F8A5872/whispers-know-but-needed-three-weeks-off-and-already-used-my-vacation-days-on-situationship-miami\" id=\"_r_a_10528729856\" width=\"459\" height=\"288\" alt=\"One of them goes: \u0026#34;Okay don\u0026#39;t judge me, but I told HR I\u0026#39;m pregnant.\u0026#34; Her friend: \u0026#34;YOU\u0026#39;RE NOT.\u0026#34; She whispers: \u0026#34;I know. But I needed three weeks off, and I already used my vacation days on a situationship in Miami.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528730112/h4762F50A/case-anyone-got-suspicious-key-is-talk-about-like-annoyed-not-excited-way-no-one-asks-see-pictures\" id=\"_r_a_10528730112\" width=\"450\" height=\"422\" alt=\"I turned my whole head. She said she photoshopped a sonogram, scheduled \u0026#34;doctor appointments,\u0026#34; and even made a baby name list in case anyone got suspicious. \u0026#34;The key is to talk about it like you\u0026#39;re annoyed, not excited. That way no one asks to see pictures.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n    \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528729088/h30540525/say-had-m-scarriage-next-month-then-rebrand-maybe-go-back-school\" id=\"_r_a_10528729088\" width=\"470\" height=\"193\" alt=\"\u0026#34;I\u0026#39;ll say I had a m scarriage next month. Then I\u0026#39;ll rebrand. Maybe go back to school.\u0026#34;\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528729600/hC6C1F9BB/both-legs-would-be-out-months-company-sending-her-flowers-weekly-etc-after-three-months-she-quit\" id=\"_r_a_10528729600\" width=\"444\" height=\"313\" alt=\"Bkbnow. Years ago a girl at my then job faked a car accident. Said she broke both legs. Would be out for months. Company was sending her flowers weekly etc. after three months she quit\" title=\"\" data-old-src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAI=\"/\u003e  \u003c/p\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003cli\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10528729344/h354C503F/paid-leave-shes-going-need-documentation-doctor-not-just-photoshopped-sonogram-or-medical-report\" id=\"_r_a_10528729344\" width=\"455\" height=\"307\" alt=\"MNConcerto ⚫ A